        "text_NjDhBm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every piece of leather we ship has a story that starts in the fields of southern Argentina, passes through 20 years of tanning tradition at Curtidos Reconquista, and ends at your bench. We import directly — no wholesalers, no markups, no compromises on quality.</p><p>That's what <em>Luxury. Simplicity. Strength.</em> means to us.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_dxaKw9": {
